headline: Stryker (SYK) Introduces Incompass Total Ankle System at AOFAS to Enhance Patient Care
summary: Stryker (SYK) recently announced the launch of its Incompass Total Ankle System, a product designed for patients with end-stage ankle arthritis, which was showcased at the 2025 American Orthopaedic Foot & Ankle Society Annual Meeting. This innovative launch could potentially support Stryker's aim to enhance clinical performance. Over the past month, Stryker's stock gained 4%, aligning with broader market trends where benchmarks like the S&P 500 and Nasdaq reached all-time highs. Market...

headline: MedtechWOMEN Announces Virginia L. Giddings as Winner of the 2025 Ferolyn Powell Award
summary: MENLO PARK, Calif., September 10, 2025--MedtechWOMEN today announced that Virginia Giddings, Ph.D., vice president of Exploration at Edwards Lifesciences, has been named the recipient of the 2025 Ferolyn Powell Leadership Award, honoring her extraordinary contributions to advancing healthcare innovation, mentoring the next generation of leaders, and fostering diversity in the medical technology industry.
